dialogues.name: ClassmateB
dialogues.content: Oh, I messed up this exam.

dialogues.name: Vincent
dialogues.content: Study on your own; don't copy homework. You'll make progress.

dialogues.name: ClassmateB
dialogues.content: How did your exam go? It must have been fine. I'm afraid to go home.

dialogues.name: Vincent
dialogues.content: I did quite average on the exam. I'm sure I'll get scolded again when I get home.
